movies.title: Marvellous
movies.plot: Dramatisation of the true story of the life of Neil "Nello" Baldwin.  Born with a mild learning disability but without the burden of social embarrassment & how his inexhaustible ability to see the good in any situation overcame any stigma society tried to label him with.
